f-element.title:
The EDR shall generate an audit data of the following auditable events: 


Start-up and shutdown of the audit functions;

All auditable events for the [not specified] level of audit; and

                [


EDR management dashboard log in activity;

Remediation commands sent to a Host Agent, affected endpoint, or network
                    devices;

EDR configuration changes;

Other auditable events

                ].
